---
layout: layouts/base.njk
---
{# Only include the syntax highlighter CSS on blog posts, included with the CSS per-page bundle #}
<style>{% include "node_modules/prismjs/themes/prism-okaidia.css" %}</style>
<style>{% include "css/prism-diff.css" %}</style>
<h1>{{ title }}</h1>

<ul class="post-metadata">
	<li><time datetime="{{ page.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ page.date | readableDate }}</time></li>
	{%- for tag in tags | filterTagList %}
	{%- set tagUrl %}/tags/{{ tag | slugify }}/{% endset %}
	<li><a href="{{ tagUrl }}" class="post-tag">{{ tag }}</a>{%- if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}</li>
	{%- endfor %}
</ul>

{# prelude for Free little Library posts #}
{% if tags.includes('FLL') %}
  <p></p>
  When I go for a run, I check the libraries. Here's what I've found recently.
{% endif %}


{# prelude for free bin posts #}
{% if tags.includes('mckays') %}
  <p></p>
  My local used book emporium has big bins of free, unwanted books. It always has some good stuff in it.
{% endif %}

<ul>
    {% for b in free_books %}
        <li> <span class="fll_booktitle"> {{b.title}}</span> by <span class="fll_bookauthor">{{b.author}}</span> </li>
    {% endfor %}
</ul>

{% if image %}
    <figure class="fll-image">
        <img src="{{ image }}" alt=" " loading="lazy">
        <figcaption></figcaption>
    </figure>
{% endif %}
{% if images %}
  {% for image in images %}
    <figure class="fll-image">
        <img src="{{ image.url }}" alt=" " loading="lazy">
        <figcaption></figcaption>
    </figure>
  {% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{{ content | safe }}


{%- if collections.FLL %}
{%- set previousPost = collections.FLL | getPreviousCollectionItem %}
{%- set nextPost = collections.FLL | getNextCollectionItem %}
{%- if nextPost or previousPost %}
<ul class="links-nextprev">
	{%- if previousPost %}<li class="links-nextprev-prev">← Previous<br> <a href="{{ previousPost.url }}">{{ previousPost.data.title }}</a></li>{% endif %}
	{%- if nextPost %}<li class="links-nextprev-next">Next →<br><a href="{{ nextPost.url }}">{{ nextPost.data.title }}</a></li>{% endif %}
</ul>
{%- endif %}
{%- endif %}
